OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA dry and largely fine Easter
OL,6,FMonday with plenty of sunshine.
OL,7,FFeeling a little warmer than the
OL,8,Fweekend, especially in the sunshine
OL,9,Fand lighter winds.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FA dry and clear night to come
OL,12,Fwith perhaps a few mist and fog
OL,13,Fpatches forming. A chilly night with
OL,14,Fperhaps a touch of frost in the
OL,15,Fcountryside.
OL,16,
OL,17,CTuesday:FAnother dry, sunny and fine
OL,18,Fday on Tuesday, although skies may
OL,19,Fturn hazy across the far west later.
OL,20,FFeeling warm, especially in the
OL,21,Fsunshine.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
